"Mr. Willkerson,

Remember to always deactivate the blue rays with the switch in this room BEFORE you deactivate the main energy field.

Accordingly, if you reactivate the energy field, the blue rays need to be activated AFTERWARDS.

In case you trigger the alarm by accident, you can turn it off by pushing the button opposite the switch. The blue rays deactivate themselves if they trigger the alarm.

If you have any questions, feel free to contact me.

George Boleston"